---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Jumbo Loans Guide"
  description="Learn about Jumbo loans, conventional loan limits, and down payment requirements for luxury homes."
>
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 pt-16 pb-24">
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-4" style="color: var(--text-primary);">
        Jumbo Loans
      </h1>
      <p class="text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto" style="color: var(--text-muted);">
        Everything you need to know about financing a high-value property that exceeds conforming loan limits.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="card p-8 sm:p-10 space-y-8">
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4" style="color: var(--text-primary);">What is a Jumbo Loan?</h2>
        <p style="color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.7;">
          A Jumbo loan is a mortgage used to finance properties that are too expensive for a conventional conforming loan. The Federal Housing Finance Agency (FHFA) sets maximum limits for conforming loans annually. If you need to borrow more than this limit, you'll need a Jumbo loan.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div class="p-5 rounded-xl border" style="background: var(--bg-surface-2); border-color: var(--border-subtle);">
          <h3 class="font-bold mb-2 text-[#f59e0b]">Stricter Requirements</h3>
          <p class="text-sm" style="color: var(--text-secondary);">Because these loans cannot be purchased by Fannie Mae or Freddie Mac, lenders take on more risk. Expect higher credit score requirements (often 700+) and lower debt-to-income limits.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-5 rounded-xl border" style="background: var(--bg-surface-2); border-color: var(--border-subtle);">
          <h3 class="font-bold mb-2 text-[#06b6d4]">Larger Down Payments</h3>
          <p class="text-sm" style="color: var(--text-secondary);">Most lenders require at least 10% to 20% down on a Jumbo loan, and you may need to show significant cash reserves (up to 12 months of payments in the bank).</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="mt-8 text-center">
        <a href="/?type=jumbo" class="inline-block px-8 py-3 rounded-lg bg-[#06b6d4] hover:bg-[#0891b2] text-white font-medium transition-colors shadow-sm">
          Calculate Jumbo Payment Now
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
